  "caption": "Modern applications often need to interact with older, complex APIs. An API wrapper acts as a translator, simplifying communication by converting modern JSON requests into legacy formats like SOAP/XML, and vice versa. This makes integration smoother and faster. Follow @byteflowlabs for daily systems & AI breakdowns.",
